caption.body: Last week, artists from Oakland’s Creative Growth Art Center Creative Growth Art Center came to visit the Airport to get a tour of "Celebrating a Vision: #ArtAndDisability". Creative Growth, which has inspired the establishment of similar programs since its founding in 1972, is one of three Bay Area organizations featured in our exhibition "Celebrating a Vision". Check out their remarkable annual Fashion Show fundraiser in this short by filmmaker Cheryl Dunn: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ffggiA6t2vE  See more art from #CreativeGrowth in "Celebrating a Vision: #ArtAndDisability", post-security, in Terminal 3. http://bit.ly/ArtAndDisability
